values: Okay, six more icons. I feel like I'm improving nicely here. All of this is HIM related in some way.. so here you go. Enjoy. There are two that look identical. The first one is transparent, the second one is not. //-- Teaser:
Just a bit more of Arch Enemy. They're icons from the music video for "We Will Rise". All except one icon are of Angela Gossow. What can I say? I like her. Lol. //-- Teaser: Enjoy.

Alright, time for a new post. In this post, I have a base of Dani Filth, bases of Dimmu Borgir, a random banner of Angela Gossow of Arch Enemy, and some Harry Potter stuff. These banners have text on them, but it's not specific as to what it has to be used for.. so you can use them for basically anything you want. //-- Teaser
This post contains three friends only banners. There are transparencies in all three of these. Two Ville Valo from HIM, and one Kaoru from Dir en Grey. //-- Teaser: . . x|[ Rissa ]|x . .

Okay, here comes the first batch of graphics. I have icons, and one friends only banner. The icons are of Dani Filth from Cradle of Filth and Angela Gossow from Arch Enemy. The friends only banner features the whole band of Arch Enemy. Comment and credit, or I'll hunt you down. :] // Teaser --

Welcome to the new graphics journal for . The old icon journal didn't seem to fit me anymore, and so I have created a new one. In fact, I rarely even updated it anymore, and I am determined to update this one more often. For now, it shall remain public. Anyone can friend it, but the very first time I catch someone using my things without credit, then it shall instantly go friends only! So be careful, and please use respect when taking my work. . . x|[ Rissa ]|x . .
